            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "instead of sending the error immediately, you'd like to check if Lua side knows about this Method?\n\n```c\nif (!p->handler.fn) {\n    //check with Lua before sending an error\n    . . .\n     send_error(channel, p->handler, p->type, p->request_id, p->unpack_error.msg);\n     api_clear_error(&p->unpack_error);\n     arena_mem_free(arena_finish(&p->arena));\n     return;\n }\n```",
